<br>
Fritz,<br>
<br>
So our past friendships mean nothing to you.  I'm not surprised, given the current opinion your compadres keep of me.  Well, alright then.<br>
<br>
Scout you may be, woodelf, but ranger you are not.  You would never find me if I did not wish you to.  However, I think I'll let you find me.  But understand this....homeless I may be now, but alone I am not. So come at me prepared or not at all.<br>
<br>
I do find myself somewhat saddened by the ease with which you throw aside our friendship, to defend people who don't even like you.  Oh, well. I rather look forward to this.<br>
<br>
~Sarhea <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usarhea.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sarhea</A> at: 12/10/01 9:40:12 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/unhjstr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>NhJstr</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_purplespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/10/01 10:30:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Open Letter to Fritz Darkweaver</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Menemas cuts open his hand, and proceeds to use the blood to scrawl the following on the back of the letter </i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
<br>
Sweet little Sarhea,<br>
<br>
Never forget that I will always be in the shadows, watching, waiting, biding my time.  When Fritz does come, do not be so foolish as to think that he will be alone.<br>
<br>
~ Id <p>Id<BR>
The true Menemas<BR>
Starspun <BR>
Firionia Vie <BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usarhea.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sarhea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle> #2 cutie ranger</span><br>  Posts: 160<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/10/01 11:12:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Open Letter to Fritz Darkweaver</span><hr size=1> Menemas,<br>
<br>
You have lost what little mind you had to begin with.  This isn't your fight. So go back into whatever corner you've crawled out of and stay out of this. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/unhjstr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>NhJstr</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_purplespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/10/01 2:06:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Open Letter to Fritz Darkweaver</span><hr size=1> Ha, silly half breed,<br>
<br>
You still lack the vision to see what is the grand scheme of things.  Perhaps soon he will teach you to tap into the rage and see what I envision.  Until that day however, even if I shared with you what I see, you could not even begin to fathom what is going on here.  <br>
<br>
So Fritz, when the day of reckoning comes, and you stand across the field from your target.  Have no fear, for I shall ensure her precious love will not interfere on her behalf.<br>
<br>
 <p>Id<BR>
The true Menemas<BR>
Starspun <BR>
Firionia Vie <BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umenemasfleetfoott.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Menemas Fleetfoott</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/10/01 2:33:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Open Letter to Fritz Darkweaver</span><hr size=1> *Menemas sighs and straightens his shoulders, tears in his eyes at the strife that has interrupted his life*<br>
<br>
My Dearest Sarhea, what have you become?  I do not wish to see you harmed, but if you must have it out with your friend Fritz so be it.  And to Id, whoever you may be, you will NOT interfere in this.  I WILL stop you.  My love and my friend will fight on even footing.  And when I come, I will not cower in the shadows.  I will let my presence be known and shout to the high heavens where the great mother resides and you, nor any other, shall interfere.  I cannot wish either of you luck in this, for I do not condone  this conflict.  All I can do is try to guarantee an even fight.  <br>
<br>
Menemas <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usarhea.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sarhea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle> #2 cutie ranger</span><br>  Posts: 162<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/10/01 2:35:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Open Letter to Fritz Darkweaver</span><hr size=1> ....Menemas? What game is this you're playing? <p><center><b><font color="#710672" face="Black Chancery" size="-1">Sarhea</font><font
face="arial" size="-1"> <br>
</b><em>Halflelven Ranger</em></font></p>
</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/unhjstr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>NhJstr</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_purplespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/10/01 2:53:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Open Letter to Fritz Darkweaver</span><hr size=1> Bah, Menemas is nothing but a weakling.  The only sounds he'll make that raise to the heavens are his screams as I finally finish him off, once and for all.  I am prepared for you, who once held me captive.  But you have forgotten me, and left me everything you could not, and did not want, and now, I shall destroy for it. <p>Id<BR>
The true Menemas<BR>
Starspun <BR>
Firionia Vie <BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usarhea.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sarhea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle> #2 cutie ranger</span><br>  Posts: 163<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/10/01 3:00:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Open Letter to Fritz Darkweaver</span><hr size=1> Look, Menemas, or what the hell ever.  You go on and fight with yourself, I've a scout to find. I'm much too busy to watch you crumble in the tiny pieces you will, so if you'll excuse me, I'll leave you with your illusions. <p><center><b><font color="#710672" face="Black Chancery" size="-1">Sarhea</font><font
face="arial" size="-1"> <br>
</b><em>Halflelven Ranger</em></font></p>
</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ufritzdarkweaver.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fritz Darkweaver</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif " BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wedgie Avenger</span><br>  Posts: 173<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/10/01 8:15:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Open Letter to Fritz Darkweaver</span><hr size=1> This isn't about you, Sarhea.  It's not about our friendship.  It's business, plain and simple.  I've a job to do, and I'm paid well to do it.  I've done it before, and I'll do it again.  The only difference now is that I've tossed aside all pretenses of doing my job in the name of Tunare.<br>
<br>
I could not find you if you did not wish to be found?  When you are older perhaps you will realize that there is nothing on the face of Norrath which escapes notice, and that information is always for sale.  Your soul may be in the shadows, but you are not.  You cannot remain hidden forever, and you should not brag of that which you are not capable.<br>
<br>
Bring your newfound love.  If he is so central to you and you to him, he should have no trouble defending you.  As for my part, I will continue as I always have.<br>
<br>
Why bring our friendship into this?  Did you think of our friendship before you killed my people?  Did you consider the implications before you chose to commit repeated murder?  I think not.  Because of our friendship, I'll make your end swift.  After all, I am only the messenger, and this is a gift you have sent to yourself.   <p>Fritz Darkweaver<BR>
Wood Elven Scout of Tunare<BR><BR>

<I>"Rich man, poor man, beggar man, thief" -- E. E. Milne</I></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ujape2lions.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jape2Lions</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 50<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/14/01 9:26:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Open Letter to Fritz Darkweaver</span><hr size=1> Ok, what's going on here? Hmm. Time to gather some info...<br>
<br>
Jepal Lions<br>
